&lt;/h1>&lt;p>&lt;img src="/imgs/img-lazy-loading.gif" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/W7S6UBiahSDKVx3KoEd4M4kyQ0ltnHymhr99w1DXDwlRoBsEwfAUt5icwUe0diaEJFgoMnX4Dl9xUUiaA0f4mLfwaw/640?wx_fmt=webp&amp;amp;from=appmsg&amp;amp;wxfrom=13" alt="图片" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>刚刚，川普在共和党初选的超级星期二中，成功地以绝对优势赢下初选，黑利宣布退选，共和党和民主党都只剩下唯一的候选人。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>2024美国选战，还是两个老头对决。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>米莱国会演讲万字全文！《向特权宣战，重建阿根廷！》</title><link>/_drafts/%E7%B1%B3%E8%8E%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%9A%E6%BC%94%E8%AE%B2%E4%B8%87%E5%AD%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87%E5%90%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9D%83%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%98%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E7%B1%B3%E8%8E%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%9A%E6%BC%94%E8%AE%B2%E4%B8%87%E5%AD%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87%E5%90%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9D%83%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%98%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="炸裂米莱国会演讲万字全文向特权宣战重建阿根廷">炸裂：米莱国会演讲万字全文！《向特权宣战，重建阿根廷！》
